<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b20Jul1938"><font color="red">20 July 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I thank you for sending me &hellip; the first corrections of the Transatlantic Review piece of W.i.P. I am posting today, as you request, 5 copies of the <i>Irish Times</i> of July 11 to Mr Joyce and one to Mr Griffin. </div>
